  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/781500/extras/af1d1a5b0783f57e0357535ce9c4c6b2.webp?t=1676775083\" width=800 height=50 /></span><br>Maybe the most addictive snake game ever. Help baby snake eat candies and become more stronger, all mystery power-ups are your best friends, they can help you and give you more power to fight against those aggressive snakes.<br><br>This game includes an adventure mode, a time trial and a challenge mode. This is a great game for any aged players. I promise you will love it in 5 minutes.<br><br><br><strong>Features</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Three game mode: Adventure, time trial and challenge.<br></li><li>Four different game scenes, 21 unique game levels.<br></li><li>Play is very simply, only need move your mouse.<br></li><li>Exciting game music and 3D sound effects.</li></ul><br><br>Other games from BD Studio Games： ",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/781500/extras/af1d1a5b0783f57e0357535ce9c4c6b2.webp?t=1676775083\" width=800 height=50 /></span><br>Maybe the most addictive snake game ever. Help baby snake eat candies and become more stronger, all mystery power-ups are your best friends, they can help you and give you more power to fight against those aggressive snakes.<br><br>This game includes an adventure mode, a time trial and a challenge mode. This is a great game for any aged players. I promise you will love it in 5 minutes.<br><br><br><strong>Features</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Three game mode: Adventure, time trial and challenge.<br></li><li>Four different game scenes, 21 unique game levels.<br></li><li>Play is very simply, only need move your mouse.<br></li><li>Exciting game music and 3D sound effects.</li></ul><br><br>Other games from BD Studio Games： ",
